<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV79">
<l>vētaṉai veṇpuri nūlaṉai viṇṇōr paravaniṉṟa</l>
<l>nātaṉai ñālam viḻuṅku manātaṉai ñālantattum</l>
<l>pātaṉaip pāṟkaṭaṟ pāmpaṇai mēṟpaḷḷi koṇṭaruḷuñ</l>
<l>cītaṉai yētoḻu vārviṇṇu ḷāriluñ cīriyarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one of the Veda, the one with a white sacred thread, the lord who stands</l>
<l>while the celestials revere [him], the one without superior who swallowed the world,</l> 
<l>the one with feet who jumped over the world, the cool one who graciously rests on the serpent bed</l>
<l>in the milk ocean, those who worship him are excellent even among those who are in heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
